immediately assigned to Enron Canada, meaning that we are directly=20
responsible for making all funding requests and all cost of borrowing=20
payments to WestLB.

2.  The initial payment on the turbines was made through WestLB for an amoun=
t=20
of US$9,000,000 on December 1, 1999.  GST was payable on US$5,000,000 of tha=
t=20
amount.

